Because I know that I am actually in the minority. 

I would love to find resources for single parents in need here on Long Island & Queens and give back. Let‚Äôs help single moms and dads that are doing their very best, but sometimes need a little more support.

I am one of the very lucky ones though. I have a support system that kicked in. My parents, my brother and sister in law, my partner - they did their best to make sure our house was in order, and the boys had what they needed. I am so grateful to be one of the lucky ones..

The absolute guilt I felt not being able to care for my children on their first days of school wrecked me. My boys started 8th & 11th grades with little fanfare from their mom who just couldn‚Äôt. I had no energy and I couldn‚Äôt control my pain.
